e Fonda  (  b. 1937 )."]}]},{"name":"de","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["‘Attainment’."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Jeanne de Cortewyle was born in 1410, in France. She had at least 1 son with Chrétien de Haze. She died in her hometown."},"et":{"1410–":"1410–Surnud","1410–Male":"1410–Surnud","1430–1490":"1430–1490","1410–Female":"1410–Surnud","1410":"1410","1430":"1430","1490":"1490","France":"Prantsusmaa","Normandy, France":"Normandie, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"1410–":"1410–Kuollut","1410–Male":"1410–Kuollut","1430–1490":"1430–1490","1410–Female":"1410–Kuollut","1410":"1410","1430":"1430","1490":"1490","France":"Ranska","Normandy, France":"Normandie, Ranska"},"fr":{"1410–":"1410–Décédée","1410–Male":"1410–Décédé","1430–1490":"1430–1490","1410–Female":"1410–Décédée","1410":"1410","1430":"1430","1490":"1490","France":"France","Normandy, France":"Normandie, France","lifeSummary":"Jeanne de Cortewyle est née en 1410, à France. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec Chrétien de Haze. Elle est décédée dans sa ville natale."},"de":{"1410–":"1410–Verstorben","1410–Male":"1410–Verstorben","1430–1490":"1430–1490","1410–Female":"1410–Verstorben","1410":"1410","1430":"1430","1490":"1490","France":"Frankreich","Normandy, France":"Normandie, Frankreich","lifeSummary":"Jeanne de Cortewyle wurde 1410 in Frankreich geboren. Sie hatte mit Chrétien de Haze mindestens 1 Sohn. Sie starb in ihrem Geburtsort."},"ht":{"1410–":"1410–Desede","1410–Male":"1410–Desede","1430–1490":"1430–1490","1410–Female":"1410–Desede","1410":"1410","1430":"1430","1490":"1490","France":"France","Normandy, France":"Normandie, France"},"hu":{"1410–":"1410–elhunyt","1410–Male":"1410–elhunyt","1430–1490":"1430–1490","1410–Female":"1410–elhunyt","1410":"1410","1430":"1430","1490":"1490","France":"Franciaország","Normandy, France":"Normandie, Franciaország"},"id":{"1410–":"1410–Telah Meninggal","1410–Male":"1410–Telah Meninggal","1430